## Status snapshot

| Metric                          | Current (cycle 26)              | L1 target                       | L2+ stretch        |
|---------------------------------|---------------------------------|---------------------------------|--------------------|
| Falsifier count                 | 6 declared, 14 PASS-equiv (Phase 1 + smoke) | 6 (+L1 cells)        | 6 (+L2/L3/L4 cells) |
| Wall (single energy() call)     | ~0.6–1.8 s (Aer cold-start jitter) | same                         | qmirror Phase 4 → ~0.1 s |
| Best E delta from H₂ E0 (analytic) | **0.4 µHa** (max_iter=80, seed=42, conv) | (LiH baseline)         | drug-target fragment |
| External cost                   | $0 (Mac local, mock LCG)       | $0–$10 (live ANU paid tier)    | TBD                |
| Cross-repo edits                | 0 committed (consumers += pending in nexus session) | as-needed | as-needed |

**Primary constraint**: Aer state-vector simulator scales as 2ⁿ in
amplitudes (n=qubits); minimal-basis H₂ = 2 qubits, LiH parity-mapped =
4 qubits, BeH₂ ≈ 6, H₂O ≈ 8, larger systems require qubit-tapering or
active-space reduction (out of pipeline scope until L3).

